{"tid":1589724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1號去港島攻略","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:32:42.000Z","uid":152689,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"42887e8df316d8b9bf721ca473883bd5648c7e43","tid":1589724,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:46:28.000Z","msg":"民陣已經宣佈左申請緊不反對通知書<br />\n宣布當日會係港島進行遊行<br />\n港鐵嘅慣例 嗰一日一定會封站<br />\n<br />\n作為一個九龍人 或者新界人<br />\n去的方法只有紅隧西隧東隧或者鐵路<br />\n但係我哋可以考慮下 可以喺紅隧嘅入口<br />\n集結一齊行過去 只要人數夠多就一定可以<br />\n一來好多巴士都會經個度市民可以喺嗰度落車跟大隊一齊過去 唔會阻塞到嗰啲想過去嘅市民<br />\n二來 只要人數夠多一定可以成事<br />\n其實而家好多人都喺度講點樣可以去到港島<br />\n我覺得呢一個係一個唔錯嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n時間就定係12點 <br />\n朝早我哋做比國際睇<br />\n夜晚再分區"},{"pid":"df5b709321c04692ad01e5381211a98486202c99","tid":1589724,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"929 101"},{"pid":"090a87e436e8619ff5eb9ec0e1169fa5d99bb4de","tid":1589724,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"7844b5867f42e7fa3149db158c58b1693c1bf60c","tid":1589724,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"929 101"},{"pid":"93e797607fe6389d42f2020dbbd2d83d72021a5c","tid":1589724,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"929 101"},{"pid":"a18c1ee093f765349ca6ade75dad02f03dfd47a5","tid":1589724,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"929 101"},{"pid":"e05a9307d75147be0ef305494b7849ba56c7ad99","tid":1589724,"uid":152689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201